        Not particle board. Not veneer. Real wood, built by hand,
        to your exact specification.
      </p>
      <div class="hero__actions">
        <a href={`tel:${business.phoneTel}`} class="btn btn-phone">Call {business.phone}</a>
        <a href="#showroom" class="btn btn-outline-cream">Visit the Showroom</a>
